<li><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_ocyWJksM2M">Part&nbsp;4 - Wifi-based Indoor Positioning System Presentation</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BzDGiRzUrLk">Part&nbsp;5 - Wifi-based Indoor Positioning System Presentation</a></li>
</ul>
